THE DAY-TO-DAY LIVES</i>

5
00:00:26,192 --> 00:00:28,494
<i>OF A FAMILY FROM
SANTA BARBARA, CALIFORNIA.</i>

6
00:00:28,528 --> 00:00:30,279
<i>THEY AGREED
TO LET A FILM CREW</i>

7
