25
00:01:50,527 --> 00:01:52,528
<i>¶ JUST HOLD ME TIGHT ¶</i>

26
00:01:52,562 --> 00:01:55,831
<i>¶ AND TELL ME
YOU'LL MISS ME ¶</i>

27
00:01:55,865 --> 00:01:58,183
<i>¶ WHILE I'M ALONE ¶</i>

28
