<i>¶ BEHIND YOU ¶</i>

40
00:02:39,275 --> 00:02:41,326
<i>¶ BUT IN YOUR DREAMS ¶</i>

41
00:02:41,377 --> 00:02:43,912
<i>¶ WHATEVER THEY BE ¶</i>

42
