<i>- PAT.
- MARY.</i>

45
00:03:22,535 --> 00:03:24,920
OH, RIGHT ON TIME.

46
00:03:24,954 --> 00:03:26,838
WHAT IS THIS ALL ABOUT?

47
00:03:26,873 --> 00:03:28,707
OH, YOU'LL SEE.

48
00:03:28,758 --> 00:03:31,493
COME, DEAR.
WE'RE SITTING RIGHT UP THERE.

49
00:03:33,663 --> 00:03:35,664
